            <h2 class="section-feedback__subtitle">Оценим и купим в любом состоянии!</h2>
            <div class="feedback-grid">
                <div class="feedback-grid__item-image">
                    <img class="feedback-grid__image" src="images/background/notebook.jpg" alt="">
